    "comprehension": null,
    "direction": null,
    "content": "<p>The correct order of decreasing stability of\nthe following carbocation is</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m3o1bvut/945dbd70-7aa3-40e4-b9e3-d60915588ca8/10f57350-a63a-11ef-a300-b723d4598e73/file-jaoe38c1m3o1bvuu.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m3o1bvut/945dbd70-7aa3-40e4-b9e3-d60915588ca8/10f57350-a63a-11ef-a300-b723d4598e73/file-jaoe38c1m3o1bvuu.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"AIIMS 2018 Chemistry - Some Basic Concepts of Organic Chemistry Question 2 English\"></p>",
    "options": [
      {
        "identifier": "A",
        "content": "II > I > III"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "B",
        "content": "II > III > I"
